<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<entry xmlns:functx="http://www.functx.com" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"
    xml:id="entry_k0yrys" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
    <form type="lemma"><orth>k˳yrys</orth></form>
    <sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
            <q>место новогоднего шабаша колдунов и ведьм, где они отчитываются о сделанном зле и
                получают задания на новые вредоносные действия</q>
        </cit><note type="comment" xml:lang=""> ()</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="">
            ()</note><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <q>the place of the New Year's Sabbath of sorcerers and witches, where they report on
                the evil done and receive tasks for new malicious actions</q>
        </cit><note type="comment" xml:lang=""> ()</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="">
        ()</note></sense>
    <re><form type="lemma"><orth>k˳yrysʒaw</orth><form type="variant"
                ><orth>k˳yrysmæʒog</orth></form></form><sense><sense><cit type="translation"
                    xml:lang="ru">
                    <q>колдун</q>
                </cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    <q>sorcerer</q>
                </cit></sense><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                    <q>ведьма</q>
                </cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    <q>witch</q>
                </cit></sense></sense></re>
    <note type="comment" xml:lang="">; </note>
    <note type="comment" xml:lang="">; </note>
    <etym xml:lang="ru">Сближается с <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>kaoirisa-</w></mentioned>
        (по <bibl><author>Bartholomae</author></bibl> — от %i*karva-%i ‘лысый’, <mentioned
            xml:lang="la"><lang/><w>calvus</w></mentioned>). По „Бундахишну“ (<bibl><biblScope>12
                25</biblScope></bibl>12 25) эта гора находилась в стране Еран-веж, т. е. в Хорезме.
        Ожидали бы ос. %i*kulis%i.%n<bibl><ref target="#ref_Gershevitch"/></bibl>, <bibl><ref
                target="#ref_BSOAS"/><biblScope xml:lang="ru">XVII 485 сл</biblScope><biblScope
                xml:lang="en">XVII 485 ff</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">It is close to <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>kaoirisa-</w></mentioned>
        (according to <bibl><author>Bartholomae</author></bibl> — from %i*karva-%i ‘bald’,
            <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/><w>calvus</w></mentioned>). According to the Bundahishn
                (<bibl><biblScope>12 25</biblScope></bibl>12 25) this mountain was located in the
        Eran-Vež country, that is, in Khwarazm. Ossetic %i*kulis%i was expected.%n<bibl><ref
                target="#ref_Gershevitch"/></bibl>, <bibl><ref target="#ref_BSOAS"/><biblScope
                xml:lang="ru">XVII 485 сл</biblScope><biblScope xml:lang="en">XVII 485
                ff</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
</entry>
